You're like a sister to me
but I'm going to get angry.

70
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:44,572
Next time,
no money, no bath!

71
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:50,572
I'll will bring the money next time.

72
00:07:50,573 --> 00:07:52,973
On my husband's grave,
I'll bring it!

73
00:07:55,660 --> 00:07:59,858
<i>It is difficult pull out a cent out of a Jew!</i>

74
00:08:00,259 --> 00:08:02,859
There're worse than the French!

75
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:08,656
Let's hope the Germans win the war
and rid us of the French!

76
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:13,492
They're going to win.

77
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,218
They're going to win.

78
