<i>"and hennaed her hair."</i>

216
00:27:48,900 --> 00:27:51,937
<i>"She has put on
her most beautiful dress"</i>

217
00:27:52,660 --> 00:27:55,891
<i>"and all her bracelets"</i>

218
00:27:56,100 --> 00:27:59,593
<i>"But she is still missing something</i>

219
00:27:59,594 --> 00:28:01,094
<i>The groom..."</i>

220
00:28:08,820 --> 00:28:10,538
My God...

221
00:28:12,340 --> 00:28:14,331
Where's the baker?

222
00:28:45,900 --> 00:28:48,653
What do we do?
- I don't know.

223
00:28:48,860 --> 00:28:50,691
They're not going to bomb us
every day.

224
00:29:20,860 --> 00:29:23,249
<i>"The Americans and the British bomb you"</i>

225
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:25,769
<i>"in order to invade your country."</i>

226
00:29:25,780 --> 00:29:29,370
<i>"They're friends of the Jews,</i>

227
00:29:29,371 --> 00:29:31,871
<i>"We're friends of the Muslims."</i>

228
00:29:34,660 --> 00:29:37,333
<i>"Show this pamphlet"</i>

229
00:29:37,540 --> 00:29:40,691
<i>"and you'll be treated as a friend."</i>

230
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:13,892
Let's go..

231
00:30:16,060 --> 00:30:18,654
-She makes couscous without salt?.
-I asked her to.

232
00:30:18,860 --> 00:30:22,648
but she's such a scatterbrain.

233
00:30:22,860 --> 00:30:26,648
Why so much oil?
I told you already.

234
00:30:26,860 --> 00:30:28,920
-Sorry. ma'am.

235
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:31,517
They never understand a thing.

236
00:30:31,520 --> 00:30:34,078
These natives are a disaster..

237
00:30:34,079 --> 00:30:36,279
Calm down.
The roundups make her edgy.

238
00:30:36,380 --> 00:30:39,497
-This is terrible service!
I'll see to it....

239
00:30:39,860 --> 00:30:42,897
-Mother, it doesn't matter!.
-You always say that.

240
00:30:43,100 --> 00:30:45,360
She hasn't given us spoons.

241
00:30:45,361 --> 00:30:47,561
It's all right. Let's eat.

242
00:30:47,562 --> 00:30:50,062
Fire her if you're not happy.

243
00:30:49,564 --> 00:30:52,359
Every meal,
we talk about the maid!

244
00:30:52,764 --> 00:30:53,860
Can we eat?

245
00:30:54,740 --> 00:30:56,698
-The meatballs are good.

246
00:30:56,700 --> 00:30:58,775
-I haven't had meat.
since the war began.

247
00:30:58,776 --> 00:31:00,076
We'll have it
at the wedding.

248
00:31:00,100 --> 00:31:02,096
We need your guest list.

249
00:31:02,097 --> 00:31:03,225
Only family.

250
00:31:02,780 --> 00:31:07,012
With this fine to pay
we need to cut back.

251
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:09,989
-I don't know how to pay.
Don't worry.

252
00:31:10,580 --> 00:31:11,990
Thank you, Raoul.

253
00:31:18,380 --> 00:31:21,338
-I'm sorry, but I will leave
after the lunch.

254
00:31:21,540 --> 00:31:23,916
-I have a patient later too.

255
00:31:24,017 --> 00:31:25,817
Why does the hospital
give you so much work?

256
00:31:25,020 --> 00:31:28,490
I'm lucky I kept my job!

257
00:31:28,700 --> 00:31:31,498
Thanks to you, Sid Mustapha.

258
00:31:31,700 --> 00:31:35,295
- God bless you.
-The pleasure is all mine, lady.

259
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:37,855
Three other doctors backed me up.

260
00:31:38,060 --> 00:31:40,972
And I left France
to be safe here!.

